text: Nukayevo () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Nukayevsky Selsoviet, Kugarchinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 298 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 25 km from Mrakovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kugarchinsky District
title: Nukayevo
